==English==

===Etymology===
Old English [[bliþe|blīþe]], from Germanic ''*bliþiz''. Cognate with Dutch [[blijde]]. Compare [[bliss]], [[Happy]].

===Pronunciation===
*{{IPA|/blaɪð/}}

